The purpose of this interventional study is to evaluate the effectiveness of the NLP PTSD protocol in the event of PPPTSD in comparison with the common practice protocol.

 The study's main hypothesis is that the implementation of both protocols will be equally effective and result in reduction of the overall PTSD level.

